      <title>韩国政党承诺使用美国比特币 ETF 来争夺选票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/south-korean-party-pledges-access-to-us-bitcoin-etfs-in-race-for-votes</link>
